            <title>[LU-5685] (cl_lock.c:1128:cl_use_try()) ASSERTION( result != -38 )</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5685</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We hit the following LBUG twice on two Lustre clients:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
